    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The mutant can separate and identify odors at a distance of up to 60 meters. It cannot be ambushed by non-plant creatures approaching from upwind, though this is different from immunity to surprise. It can track any trail less than a day old across any surface except water. Once it has encountered another being, it can later identify objects and locations associated with that being, such as possessions or campsites.</p>"
